name: Dancing through the dreams
description:
I could write millions of things,
like, i've seen you open your eyes for the first time, i've seen you smile for the first time, crawl, walk, talk....
I love your amusement for everything , your happiness is so contagious that even a sad soul like mine sparkle when you're around me. I would love to give you everything: the sun, the moon, the stars, the sky full of dreams, i would love to give you all the happiness of this world, and sugar to make your dreams sweeter. 
I love you, 
Just keep dancing through your dreams
